{"tid":789439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Gobee.bike執笠唔退餘額　苦主入稟勝訴獲賠$30","createTime":"2018-08-22T08:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T09:10:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b1875f2eeea7a2be8766bb187a98acf2dc070b94","tid":789439,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"Gobee.bike上月突然宣布結業，稱用戶可於一星期內繼續使用單車，直至充值餘額用盡為止，及可於8月10日前於應用程式申請退還按金，惟部分用戶投訴尚有餘額未全數發還，不少苦主擬入稟索償。民間組織「沙田脈搏」召集人林宇星，早前入稟小額錢債審裁處，向Gobee.bike的母公司索償充值餘額30港元。由於被告人一方缺席聆訊，審裁官判林勝訴，獲賠30港元以及30港元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n申索人林宇星，被告人Mysharedbike Limited(自行車快樂有限公司)。據入稟狀指，Mysharedbike Limited及Gobee.bike於今年7月10日宣布清盤，<span style=\"color: red;\">聲稱只退還按金，餘額則鼓勵用家於公司應用程式於同月17日停用前使用，而所有餘額不會退還。申索人於7月10日開始，多次使用嘗試解鎖該公司的單車，惜每次掃描單車QR code，電話亦顯示「This bike has been reported as broken」(單車已損毀)，令申索人無法在限期前使用餘下的充值額。</span><br />\n<br />\n入稟狀續指，被告人於今年7月10日訂立了使用限期至同月17日，街上的單車數量卻少之又少，而且有關公司並無保障所有單車在無壞車情況下給用家使用，因此申索人認為被告人沒有履行服務承諾，遂入稟索償。<br />\n<br />\n林宇星庭外表示，至今聯絡上約100名苦主稱無法取回充值餘額，平均涉款約50港元，由數港元至500港元不等，由於金額小，因此對於申索「啲人未必願意走出嚟」。但經過今次勝訴後，林冀Gobee.bike可承諾向用家退還餘額，否則若需要其他苦主作第二輪申索亦浪費公帑。<br />\n<br />\n林又指，至今未能與Gobee.bike的負責人Raphael Cohen對話，冀透過今次申索與對方商討，「想知有冇機會退餘額，如果退唔到，係咪可以抬架車走？」林質疑Gobee.bike<span style=\"color: red;\">「以共享經濟為名目，集資後突然撤資、捲款潛逃」</span>，是不負責任、開壞先例。"},{"pid":"c68da1a9b25e3717ab630ca2b509a28ce9b3193f","tid":789439,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344c8e099e8af351ffa124299a95a935490eb2d5","tid":789439,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"大生意"},{"pid":"8e6b58d088fe3ddaf96f218d9ba48c950fd34c88","tid":789439,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68da1a9b25e3717ab630ca2b509a28ce9b3193f","tid":789439,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cce4643c1345687d6d0c20a573c9571de7976b","tid":789439,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:03:45.000Z","msg":"$30+30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7134fc0b9ee3c1f38022f5c73472d8a988d7de20","tid":789439,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IQpWsVj585xcGwyi4mU7ng--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hk01_725/6f26c4ba4d16428a94a6efeb8aef8935\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIQpWsVj585xcGwyi4mU7ng--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fhk01_725%2F6f26c4ba4d16428a94a6efeb8aef8935&h=125eeaad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf8b4a1710388616df5e1f688d6b0cb248701fc","tid":789439,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7134fc0b9ee3c1f38022f5c73472d8a988d7de20","tid":789439,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IQpWsVj585xcGwyi4mU7ng--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hk01_725/6f26c4ba4d16428a94a6efeb8aef8935\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIQpWsVj585xcGwyi4mU7ng--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zen